Comedian Bernard Manning chooses Mother Theresa of Calcutta. With Humphrey Carpenter. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? From October 2002. Show less